Subject: drm/xe: Move system memory management init to earlier point in probe
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 1ccd68e967f13a584bf3d45a58865afb0abbf2a4
